e: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; height: auto; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\" width=\"400\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n南投中興新村隱藏版美食~ 「南京老戴脆皮臭豆腐」</div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n每週只營業五、六、日三天，從下午兩點開始營業，賣完就打烊休息囉~</div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; color: teal; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; color: teal; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">地址：南投縣南投市光明一路60號</span></div>\r\n<h4 style=\"border: 0px; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 1.25em; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: 1em; margin: 1.2em 0px 0.3em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; color: blue; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">《南投。橋頭邊肉圓》</span></h4>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<img alt=\"DSC 3081\" class=\"g-resize\" height=\"268\" id=\"g-item-id-7605\" src=\"https://p.cutebox.org/var/resizes/%E3%84%A1%E5%92%BF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F/natochoto/DSC_3081.jpg?m=1455117106\" style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; height: auto; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\" width=\"400\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n超過50年以上歷史的「橋頭邊肉圓」，是南投人最愛的在地美食</div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n前陣子還獲選為台灣小吃百大名店</div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n一起來吃看看這南投人熱愛的肉圓有什麼獨特的魅力吧!!</div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; color: teal; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; color: teal; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">地址：南投市三和二路2號</span></div>\r\n<h4 style=\"border: 0px; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 1.25em; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: 1em; margin: 1.2em 0px 0.3em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; color: blue; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">《南投。老胡麵館》</span></h4>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<img height=\"304\" src=\"https://p.cutebox.org/var/resizes/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC%E7%9B%B8%E7%89%87/%E7%B8%AE%E5%9C%96%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA/R0011336.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; height: auto; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\" width=\"400\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16.0016px;\">除了喝酸梅湯，當然還得吃正餐囉!!! 本來我已經看好要吃鍋燒意麵了，小丹尼硬是要辜狗一下</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16.0016px;\">r />最後就到這個擠滿人的麵店了，來到這裡一定要分工合作，找座位、抽號碼牌、點餐</span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; color: teal; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px; color: #111111; font-family: &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 16.0016px; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.75em; margin-top: 0.75em; padding: 0px; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n<span style=\"border: 0px; color: teal; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">地址：南投市中興新村光華路98號</span></div>\r\n', 1, '2017-12-15', '南投1');
INSERT INTO `blog` (`Id`, `Title`, `Content`, `Member_id`, `Date`, `Pic`) VALUES
(2, '日本沖繩行程推薦-五天四夜食記遊記-自由行', '<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">沖繩是日本最南的縣，首府為那霸市，沖繩也是日本唯一亞熱帶氣溫的一個縣</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">從台灣坐飛機只需要一個半小時的飛行時間即可到達，算是一個很棒的出國首選</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">由於沖繩都市單軌鐵路能到達的景點有限，想要暢遊沖繩各景點還是以租車自駕最方便</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">北部的沖縄美ら海水族館、中部的美國村、南部的玉泉洞和波上宮都是一個很棒的景點</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">沖繩的美食也相當的多，通堂拉麵、暖暮拉麵、oHacorte水果塔、波布食堂和傑克牛排</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">喜歡逛街的朋友首推那霸市區的國際通，所有的好吃美食和記念品特產這裡通通都有唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">台灣虎航的航班時間是早去早回，早上六點從台灣出發，回程是早上十點半到達台灣</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">訂機票的時候會有輕裝旅行(Light)、超值組合(Combo)和靈活及舒適之選(FlexiCombo)</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">像我們一樣選擇輕裝旅行(Light)選項的朋友，手提行李總重量不可超過 10 公斤</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">台灣虎航的登機門就在最遠的B1R，到了登機時間還需要坐接駁車到停機坪自行上飛機</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">飛行時間大約是一個半小時就會到達沖繩那霸國際機場了，真的是相當的近唷！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">大約一個半小時的飛行時間，我們到達了沖繩那霸國際機場</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">由於日本沖繩比台灣快一個小時，所以到達機場後記得要調整一下時間</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">拿取託運行李和入國審查的位置在三樓，可能是淡季的關係，我們15分鐘就出關了</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">出關後回到一樓會有觀光案內所和LAWSON便利商店，觀光案內所有超多的觀光資訊</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">想要搭單軌列車或是要坐租車業者接駁車的朋友，還要自行走到另一棟國內線才行唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/671136858\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩美食|炒飯組合午餐菜單|琉球新麺通堂 小禄本店\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1482509008-2715959650.jpg?v=1482509049\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩美食|炒飯組合午餐菜單|琉球新麺通堂 小禄本店\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間琉球新麺通堂 小禄本店是網路上很多朋友都推薦的沖繩美食之一</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">他們的拉麵口味有分成比較濃郁的男味和比較清淡的女味，二種都相當好味</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">像我們一樣自駕開車來的朋友，可以停在他們的專用停車場，又或者坐單軌列車來也可以</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">推薦琉球新麺通堂的午餐菜單，平日中午限定，有炒飯組合和煎餃組合二種</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">雖說男味拉麵是比較重口味的豚骨拉麵，但是吃起來卻不會太鹹，非常的好吃唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這次的日本沖繩四日遊，我們在台灣就先在KLOOK 客路訂購了日本7天上網SIM卡</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">Dot 5 x Freetel 全日游 日本7天上網SIM卡使用的是NTT docomo 的系統</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">使用LINE、FB、WhatsApp、Kakao Talk和WeChat這五大社群APP是不計流量的</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">在網路上訂購完後就會郵寄到府，到了沖繩那霸機場就可以直接換上新SIM卡直接上網唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">一般出國用的上網卡大都是有期限的，像是五天上網卡或是七天上網卡</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">但是這張EZ Nippon 日本通 5GB上網卡非常的特別，針對的是長期旅行的朋友</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">使用期限是自啟用日起至次月月底止，大約可用30天到60天左右，或5GB用完為止</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">如果朋友們要去日本長期旅遊或是自助旅行蜜月一個多月的話，這張就非常適合唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/672094728\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】國家指定登錄有形文化財|沖繩魅力通通集聚一堂|玉泉洞 王國村 太鼓舞\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1483361982-1712341232.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】國家指定登錄有形文化財|沖繩魅力通通集聚一堂|玉泉洞 王國村 太鼓舞\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">如果是第一次來沖繩的朋友，非常推薦來這位於沖繩南部的沖繩世界文化王國玉泉洞</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這裡有國家指定登錄有形文化財的琉球古民家聚落、30萬年歲月的天然紀念物玉泉洞</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">還有最不能錯過每天的 SUPER EISA 太鼓舞表演和毒蛇大戰貓鼬的表演秀…等</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">是一個來沖繩自助旅行非常推薦的景點，還沒來過的朋友可以安排到自己的行程當中唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/672496173\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩迴轉壽司|美國村美食|美國村グルメ迴轉壽司市場美浜店\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1483675087-4095798563.jpg?v=1483675116\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩迴轉壽司|美國村美食|美國村グルメ迴轉壽司市場美浜店\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間位於美國村對面的美國村グルメ迴轉壽司市場，是很多朋友在網路上都推薦的名店</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">如果行程中有安排到沖繩美國村坐摩天輪的朋友，可以來這裡享用美味的迴轉壽司大餐</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這裡的迴轉壽司價格並不會特別便宜，但是食材的新鮮程度是毋庸置疑的</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">入坐之後除了可以直接取用迴轉帶上面的壽司，還可以直接使用座位旁的觸控螢幕點餐</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">吃飽喝足之後工作人員會拿著一台機器直接感應桌上的空盤就可以算出消費盤數和金額唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/672532797\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩自由行自駕租車|租車費用 高速公路過路費 加油費用分享|Times Car  RENTAL\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1483699231-700242641.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩自由行自駕租車|租車費用 高速公路過路費 加油費用分享|Times Car  RENTAL\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這次的四天三夜冬季沖繩自助旅行，我們從 KLOOK 客路上預訂了八人座汽車出租</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">客路的汽車出租有分成旺季和淡季，大家在選擇的時候要注意旅行的日期別選錯了</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">車輛的選擇有C1-5人座-1300cc、C2-5人座-1500cc和C3-8人座這三種車型</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">我們同行的旅伴總共有六個人，行李總共有六個20吋的行李箱，C3-8人座剛剛好</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">出了沖繩那霸國際機場之後，就要先自行走到旁邊另一棟國內線機場前，接駁車會在那裡</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">接駁車帶我們到Times Car RENTAL的接待處，辦理好租車手續之後就可以出發了</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">在那四天當中，我們從最南部的沖繩世界到最北部的海洋博公園通通都是靠車上的導航</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">如果有路經高速公路的話，請記得不要走ETC車道，而是要走一般車道直接付過路費</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">Times Car RENTAL的車輛都是滿油出租的，所以還車的時候記得要先去加滿油再還車唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/672663675\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩美國村住宿|有停車場 三房一廳一衛|超高級公寓Airbnb\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1483803396-1848786650.jpg?v=1483803426\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩美國村住宿|有停車場 三房一廳一衛|超高級公寓Airbnb\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這次的沖繩之旅是一個五星級(有省錢)之旅，所以我們的住宿就在Airbnb上面尋找</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">第一個晚上我們住宿在美國村附近，因為晚上就可以去逛逛有聖誕節氣氛的美國村</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">隔天去北部的沖繩美麗海水族館也會近一些，隔天早餐也可以在美國村解決</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間超高級公寓有三房二廳一衛，最多可以住進10位房客，還有專屬停車位給自駕的朋友</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">不過 Airbnb 大部份是見不到民宿主人的，都是要到一個特定的地點去拿鑰匙</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">雖然住宿地點不錯、房價便宜房間也相當舒適，不過在入住的時候還是有一些些不方便呀</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/673368402\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】陳漢典推薦的沖繩美國村美食|Benson\'s漢堡熱狗店\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1484410586-3214253125.jpg?v=1484410598\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】陳漢典推薦的沖繩美國村美食|Benson\'s漢堡熱狗店\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間位於沖繩美國村的Benson\'s 漢堡熱狗店，可是很多朋友都相當推薦的沖繩美食之一</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">連沖繩達人史丹利、陳漢典和LULU都曾經來過並簽名放在店裡，逛累了可以來休息一下</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">餐點有各式各樣的漢堡和熱狗，店裡的第一名就是 Californian 加利福尼亞熱狗</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">加利福尼亞熱狗使用的是鬆軟的熱狗麵包夾入熱狗後再淋上牛肉肉醬，相當的香辣好吃唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/673684965\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩美國村早餐|限量版冬季飲品|Starbucks 美浜店\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1484635309-1936941109.jpg?v=1484635338\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩美國村早餐|限量版冬季飲品|Starbucks 美浜店\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">如果來沖繩住宿在美國村附近的話，推薦可以來這間 Starbucks Coffee 美浜店吃早餐</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">我們來的時候剛好是聖誕節，他們有推出限量冬季飲品 Snow Pecan Nut Latte</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">來這裡除了可以吃到簡單美味的早餐外，有在收集星巴克杯子的朋友可以順便看看杯子唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/673948674\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩免費景點|無料沖兒海豚劇場|海洋博覽公園\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1484932893-1363598277.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩免費景點|無料沖兒海豚劇場|海洋博覽公園\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">在還沒去沖繩海洋博覽公園之前，原以為跟其他海洋公園一樣，都是在門口就會收門票的</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">但是一去才知道，原來收門票的只有沖繩美麗海洋水族館，除此之外通通都是免費入場的</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">像是翡翠海灘、兒童探險樂園、夕陽廣場、沖兒海豚劇場、海牛館和海龜館通通都是無料</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">特別要注意的是海豚劇場的表演時間，建議各位朋友到達之後先確認時間再去各點遊玩唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/674203242\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩景點推薦|沖繩海洋博公園 美ら海水族館|KLOOK 客路網路購票更便宜\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1485191720-619366080.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩景點推薦|沖繩海洋博公園 美ら海水族館|KLOOK 客路網路購票更便宜\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">沖繩海洋博公園以及美ら海水族館都是去沖繩自助非常推薦的景點之一</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">喜歡海洋生物的朋友，如果來到美ら海水族館，一定會流連忘返</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">現場購票要日幣1850元，建議各位朋友可以先上 KLOOK 客路網路購票只要台幣483元</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">總共有四層樓的美ら海水族館，遊玩的時間大約要四個小時，尤其是黑潮之海區域</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這裡除了可以觀賞到各式各樣的海洋生物之外，更不能錯過的就是水槽解說以及餵食解說</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">美麗海劇場和黑潮探險也是非常推薦的，還沒來過的朋友快安排進入自己的行程當中吧</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/674442147\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通住宿|有停車場 近牧志站|三房透天Airbnb\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1485490833-3082125637.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通住宿|有停車場 近牧志站|三房透天Airbnb\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這次的沖繩之旅四天三夜有二個晚上我們都住在這間國際通牧志站附近的 Airbnb</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">會挑選這間有幾個原因：有三間房間、有專屬停車場、離國際通走路只要三分鐘</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">最重要的是，房間相當實惠，每個人的預算可以控制在千元以內，是一個相當棒的選擇</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/674641740\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通美食推薦|九州拉麵票選第一位|暖暮拉麵那霸店\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1485877248-833466713.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通美食推薦|九州拉麵票選第一位|暖暮拉麵那霸店\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間曾在2002年獲得FBS舉辦的「九州拉麵總選舉」第一位的暖暮拉麵</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">是我們這次來沖繩排定的必嘗美食之一，在沖繩一共有六間分店</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">暖暮拉麵的種類並不多，總共有六種拉麵種類，不過麵的粗細、硬度、濃淡都可以選擇</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">除了拉麵之外，還有溫泉玉子飯、豚玉飯、明太子飯和博多一口餃子可以選擇</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">當天我們到的是暖暮拉麵那霸牧志店，門口有長長的排隊人龍，建議不要太餓時過來</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">暖暮拉麵的湯頭和叉燒真的相當迷人，博多一口餃子也相當推薦，外皮脆口內餡多汁唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/674840757\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通居酒屋|串燒關東煮泡盛通通有|鳥炭串燒居酒屋\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1486094982-958225886.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通居酒屋|串燒關東煮泡盛通通有|鳥炭串燒居酒屋\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間位於沖繩國際通、暖暮拉麵和單軌電車美榮橋站中間的鳥炭串燒居酒屋</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">是一間相當有日式風格的居酒屋，非常適合來沖繩旅行時，晚上想喝點小酒的好所在</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">鳥炭的用餐環境小小的、窄窄的、髒髒的，但是在裡面吃點串燒、喝點小酒卻相當自在</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">推薦他們的綜合串燒(10本1000円)和綜合關東煮(8種750円)，味道相當的美味好吃唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/675051273\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通|平和通商店街|那霸市第一牧志公設市場\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1486271572-2878604338.jpg?v=1486271587\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通|平和通商店街|那霸市第一牧志公設市場\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">來到沖繩旅行，除了可以到國際通逛街之外，平和通商店街和第一牧志公設市場也很好逛</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">平和通商店街比較多個性小店，想要挖寶的朋友，到平和通商店街比較有機會買到特別的</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">那霸市第一牧志公設市場是個吃飯的好選擇，一樓是各式海鮮，海鮮可以買到二樓用餐唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/675515361\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通牧志公設市場美食|傳統鄉土菓子|琉球菓子処 琉宮のサーターアンダギー\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1486661066-4038864752.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通牧志公設市場美食|傳統鄉土菓子|琉球菓子処 琉宮のサーターアンダギー\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間位於沖繩國際通、牧志公設市場附近的琉球菓子專賣店，是一間非常推薦的伴手禮店</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">他們的招牌就是サーターアンダギー(砂糖天婦羅)，是一種油炸的傳統鄉土菓子甜品</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">「サーターアンダギー」就是台灣的開口笑，吃起來表面脆口，裡面卻相當鬆軟</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">サーターアンダギー有不同的口味，有原味、黑糖、椰子和芝麻，來沖繩一定要吃吃看唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/675632517\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通早餐|牧志公設市場巷弄美食|亞砂呂琉球家庭料理\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1486784987-626217967.jpg?v=1486785015\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通早餐|牧志公設市場巷弄美食|亞砂呂琉球家庭料理\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間亞砂呂琉球家庭料理的位置就在那霸市第一牧志公設市場附近的巷弄內</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">如果想吃和食早餐的話，推薦可以來亞砂呂試試，他們的豆腐味噌湯真是好喝</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">除了和食洋食早餐之外，他們也有提供各種手作琉球料理，是一間非常道地的料理小店唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/675683280\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩蕎麥麵|中文菜單  まちぐゎー案内所|ニライカナイ食堂\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1486827071-3804011064.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩蕎麥麵|中文菜單  まちぐゎー案内所|ニライカナイ食堂\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間位於沖繩那霸市區國際通與牧志公設市場附近的ニライカナイ食堂</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">是一間沖繩大眾料理食堂，對面就是まちぐゎー案内所 ゆっくる(觀光案內所)</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">他們有提供中文菜單，不用擔心點餐問題，餐點價格從日幣350元到850元不等</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">推薦沖繩蕎麥麵便宜又美味，加一些沖繩特產辣椒油會更加美味唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/676117965\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩限定轉蛋|新版 沖縄フィギュアみやげ|OKINAWA FIGURE MIYAGE\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1487222285-4013652153.jpg?v=1487222316\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩限定轉蛋|新版 沖縄フィギュアみやげ|OKINAWA FIGURE MIYAGE\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">每當到日本各地旅行，我們總是會找當地的限定轉蛋當作旅行的記念品之一</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">到了沖繩當然也不例外，我們在國際通就轉了這款「新版 沖繩フィギュアみやげ」轉蛋</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這款轉蛋是2016年7月16日發行的，最主要的是新增了前 WBA 世界次特輕量級冠軍</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">出身石垣島的「具志堅用高」轉蛋和沖繩傳統藝能-太鼓舞</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這款沖繩フィギュアみやげ轉蛋的特色是表現出沖繩景點、物產和文化…等</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">各位朋友如果有來沖繩旅行的話，推薦可以轉一顆當作一個特別的旅行記念品吧</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/676362864\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩下午茶|沖繩自駕推薦景點|oHacorte水果塔フルーツタルト專門店\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1487438679-2378405724.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩下午茶|沖繩自駕推薦景點|oHacorte水果塔フルーツタルト專門店\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">oHacorte 是沖繩一間水果塔フルーツタルト專門店，目前他們在沖繩有五間分店</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">其中最推薦的就是oHacorte港川店本店，港川店就位於浦添市港川的外人住宅街內</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">港川店除了有各式各樣美味水果塔之外，店內還有販賣一些日本經典家居用品生活雜貨</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">2009年開業的 oHacorte 水果塔專賣店，使用的都是當季多汁水果當作水果塔的食材</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">每一個水果塔都像一個美麗炫爛的珠寶盒，雖附有刀叉可以方便食用但卻難以下手呀！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/676857063\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩免費景點|舊官幣小社 沖繩總鎮守 波上宮\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1487859611-3305385563.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩免費景點|舊官幣小社 沖繩總鎮守 波上宮\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">波上宮就位於沖繩縣那霸市波之上海灘旁，是一個很不錯的沖繩免費景點</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">來這除了可以參拜沖繩總鎮守 波上宮之外，還可以到波之上海灘玩玩水</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">波上宮有提供參拜者專用停車場，對於來沖繩有自駕的朋友相當的方便唷！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/677003253\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩超大份量美食推薦|大胃王快來挑戰|波布食堂 波布お食事処\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1488031979-238723237.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩超大份量美食推薦|大胃王快來挑戰|波布食堂 波布お食事処\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間位於沖繩那霸港口邊的波布食堂，是一間非常推薦來沖繩自助必訪的大份量餐廳</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">因為波布食堂的主要客群是在港口工作的工人或員工，所以他們的餐點都是超大份量</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">波布食堂的門口設有停車位，對於自駕的朋友非常方便，直接把車停在餐廳門口就行</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">非常推薦來波布食堂一定要試試他們的的肉そば(豬肉蕎麥麵)和チャーハン(炒飯)</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">剛拿到豬肉蕎麥麵的時候覺得超級壯觀的，一大碗的蕎麥麵上面推滿了炒好的肉和菜</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">高度大約有20公分高，吃完真的超級滿足的，還沒吃過的朋友，把波布食堂排入行程吧</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/677626293\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩牛排| SINCE1953 沖繩第一間牛排館|傑克牛排館 Jack\'s Steak House\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1488553519-3277400377.jpg?v=1488553547\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩牛排| SINCE1953 沖繩第一間牛排館|傑克牛排館 Jack\'s Steak House\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間沖繩傑克牛排館 Jack\'s Steak House，是我們來沖繩前就安排進行程美食清單內</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">成立於西元1953年第二次世界大戰後的傑克牛排館，當時深受美軍和當地人的喜愛</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">自駕的朋友不用擔心停車的問題，傑克牛排館有專用停車場，還會有服務人員協助停車</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">菜單推薦第一名的特選烤里脊牛排或是第二名的紐約客牛排，附餐有白飯或是麵包可以選</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">各位朋友如果來沖繩旅遊，推薦來這裡試試有六十多年歷史的沖繩老字號人氣牛排館唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/677684610\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩伴手禮|超多試吃品 見學生產工廠|御菓子御殿 國際通松尾店\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1488635663-3959391345.jpg?v=1488636392\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩伴手禮|超多試吃品 見學生產工廠|御菓子御殿 國際通松尾店\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">來到沖繩那霸國際通，如果想買土產伴手禮的話，非常推薦這間御菓子御殿國際通松尾店</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間御菓子御殿國際通松尾店是以首里城為主題，每一樣伴手禮幾乎都有提供試吃品</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">在國際通逛累了，御菓子御殿也有提供一個舒適的用餐環境，可以吃個甜點飲料休息一下</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">最後面還有御菓子御殿的生產工廠，可以看到紅芋塔是如何被生產出來的，相當有趣唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/678378372\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通免費景點|沖繩美麗海水族館直營店 うみちゅらら\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1489148731-1606120997.jpg?v=1489148744\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩國際通免費景點|沖繩美麗海水族館直營店 うみちゅらら\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">這間位於沖繩國際通上的沖繩美麗海水族館直營店(アンテナショップ ”うみちゅらら”)</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">是一間相當推薦的沖繩國際通免費景點，這裡有一整排的迷你水族箱，花園鰻真的超可愛</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">還有沖繩美麗海水族館的人氣紀念品，像是超大型的鯨鯊娃娃和限定版雪鹽黑糖和菓子</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">逛街逛累了也可以到這裡的草果菜 Cafe 喝一杯沖</span><span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">繩在地的長命草琉球藥草蔬果汁唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"http://dong1104.pixnet.net/album/photo/679166988\" style=\"color: #335e6b; text-decoration-line: none;\"><img alt=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩那霸國際通吃喝玩樂一次滿足|国際通り散策\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/dong1104/1489845568-1645624738.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"【沖繩自助/自由行】沖繩那霸國際通吃喝玩樂一次滿足|国際通り散策\" /></a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">國際通 沖繩縣那霸市約1.6公里的大街，國際通也是那霸市最繁華的商業街</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">想要吃美食、買土產、體驗三味線、買紀念品、看喜劇表演、逛屋台村通通有</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">很多土產店都相當有特色，進去要有掏空錢包的覺悟，因為紀念品實在是太可愛了</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">喜歡純逛街拍照的朋友，千萬不要錯過街邊特色擺設，像是小拳王和風獅爺都好好拍唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">那霸機場是日本的第二種機場，整個機場只有一條跑道，機場旁還有個嘉手納空軍基地</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">那覇機場國際線旅客航站大廈總共有四層樓，一、二樓是出入境大廳和一些紀念品商店</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #7f7f7f; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: purple; font-size: 12pt;\">三、四樓是餐廳、禮拜室和機場觀景台，想要吃早餐的朋友可以到一樓的LAWSON商店唷</span></div>\r\n', 2, '2017-12-15', '沖繩2');
INSERT INTO `blog` (`Id`, `Title`, `Content`, `Member_id`, `Date`, `Pic`) VALUES
(3, '台中2天1夜旅程', '<span style=\"color: #363636; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;verdana&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot;; font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-family: , serif;\">最近去台中好像在走造咖</span>XD<span style=\"font-family: , serif;\">，幾乎每個月都會造訪一次！</span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;verdana&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot;; font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-family: , serif;\">跑了不少地方、吃了不少美食、雖然住台北，卻也深深喜歡上這個舒服的城市，印像中好像都沒有寫過懶人包的遊記，規劃了一個</span>2<span style=\"font-family: , serif;\">天</span>1<span style=\"font-family: , serif;\">夜台中之旅來跟大家分享，而且不少間還是我剛收藏的口袋名單呦！<br /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體;\"><span style=\"font-family: , serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: 新細明體;\"><br /><span style=\"font-family: &quot;comic sans ms&quot; , sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/fairylolita/1368019296-698283465.gif\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Day1</span></strong>&nbsp;台中<span style=\"font-family: , serif;\">第二市場<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong>台中刑務所演武場<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong></span>林記花蓮瑞穗臭豆腐<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong></span>福芳號<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong></span>金福氣南洋食堂</span>(<span style=\"font-family: , serif;\">台中崇德總店</span>)<span style=\"font-family: , serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong></span>吳留手串燒居酒屋</span>(<span style=\"font-family: , serif;\">台中崇德店</span>)<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: , serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong></span></span>芭蕾城市渡假旅店 VillaBallet<br /><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Day2</strong></span>&nbsp;花夏入室 Fasha Room<span style=\"color: red;\">→</span>范特喜微創文化 綠光計畫<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></span></span>短腿ㄚ鹿<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></span></span>Offer Make 造堡<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></span></span>白日夢 Day Dream<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></span></span>逢甲夜市</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-family: &quot;arial&quot; , &quot;verdana&quot; , &quot;tahoma&quot;; font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><br /></span></span></span></span>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffff99;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【行程規劃】</span>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Day1</span></strong>&nbsp;台中<span style=\"color: #363636;\"><span style=\"font-family: , serif;\">第二市場<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong>台中刑務所演武場<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong></span>林記花蓮瑞穗臭豆腐<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong></span>福芳號<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong></span>金福氣南洋食堂</span>(<span style=\"font-family: , serif;\">台中崇德總店</span>)<span style=\"font-family: , serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong></span>吳留手串燒居酒屋</span>(<span style=\"font-family: , serif;\">台中崇德店</span>)<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: , serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></strong></span></span>芭蕾城市渡假旅店 VillaBallet&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482387810464_351\" src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5613/31650585752_2638fa8cbf_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #5b5b5b; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #855a40;\"><strong>台中第二市場<br />店址：台中市中區三民路2段87號<br />營業時間：AM 7：00 ～ PM 20：00</strong></span></span><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">如果你喜歡傳統的中式早餐，那麼我要大力推薦這些隱藏在市場裡面的美食，其中最具名氣的，莫過於王記菜頭粿糯米腸，聽說這可是老台中人最喜歡的早餐之一呦！軟綿綿的菜頭粿、再加上半熟蛋及糥米腸，配上一碗熱湯就整個大滿足，此外李海爌肉飯、阿嬤Ａ相思麵也不錯，如果你來到第二市場，那麼絕對要來一杯永遠都在排隊的老賴紅茶，古早味碳香交織著細碎冰塊，好喝到我們每次下台中，還都會特地繞過來買個幾瓶回台北過過癮：）</span><span style=\"color: #5b5b5b; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #855a40;\"><strong><br /></strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #5b5b5b; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #855a40;\"><strong><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482387814125_355\" src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5540/31650585572_f46bc768d9_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #5b5b5b; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #855a40;\"><strong>台中刑務所演武場<br />地址：台中市西區林森路33號</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #5b5b5b; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #855a40;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">飽餐一頓之後，接下來可以到台中刑所演武場放風一下，對於喜歡日式建築、亦或熱衷拍照的朋友，我想應該都會愛上這裡！這是台中市目前僅存的日製時期武道館建築，專供刑務所司獄官練武的地方，大心的是，不需要門票就可以免費參觀呦！假日時遊客如織，整個好不熱鬧，大推園內具有洗滌身心、清淨放鬆的心行館，目前以茶藝館的模式在經營，你也可以坐在這裡享受另一種日式風情的午后時光。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 新細明體; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #855a40;\"><strong><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482387817050_353\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/262/31650585382_fd7502b51b_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 新細明體; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">林記 花蓮瑞穗臭豆腐<br />電話：04-2211-3042<br />店址：台中市自由路三段151號<br />營業時間：PM 14：00 ～ 19：00(周二公休)</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 新細明體; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><span style=\"color: #5b5b5b; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #855a40;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">如果說到台中好吃前三名的臭豆腐，那麼這間座落於自由路上的林記花蓮瑞穗臭豆腐，絕對是大多數人都會想到的一家，外衣炸得酥酥脆脆、表層還有冒著油炸之後的小泡泡痕跡，光是賣相就給人十足可口的美味感覺，內餡飽滿多汁，佛心來著的老闆，還免費提供紅茶跟熱湯讓客人們無限暢飲呢！</span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: , serif;\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong>福芳號 |&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/food.fun.no1/\" style=\"color: #333333; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">FB</span></a></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong>電話：04-23282399</strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong>店址：台中市西區美村路一段22號(全家旁邊)</strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong>營業時間：AM 9：00 ～ PM 21：00</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">今年九月才開幕的福芳號，才沒幾個月光景，立馬攀升為ＩＧ上打卡的新景點！實在是那剛推出的草莓季限定商品長得太美麗，叫人看了直呼少女心都要噴發啦！目前草莓系列有「戀上草莓騷莎」、「莓好滋味」兩種，其實其它款飲品也長得很動人，像咖啡抹茶拿鐵就是時下很流行的漸層色系，想要跟你的ＩＧ有很多按讚數？！那麼來這裡準沒錯！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482387821908_369\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/434/31650584322_eba69a94aa_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: , serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">金福氣南洋食堂(台中崇德總店)&nbsp;</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">電話：04-22367060</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">店址：台中市北屯區崇德路二段67號</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">營業時間：AM 10：00 ～ PM 20：30</span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">還記得幾個月前，我寫了一篇彩虹懶人包，那時候只要知道哪兒有彩虹美食的蹤跡，總耐不住我的衝動而立馬跑去插旗，這間金福氣南洋食堂收在我的口袋名單已經有好一陣子了，趁著這次到台中，當然也不能錯過它囉！包著彩虹乳酪的三明治，幾乎是裡面的必點款，號稱可以牽絲牽到１００公分，別說是拍照了，連玩起來也很有趣味耶！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482387823791_368\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/728/31650584602_0c71c11b45_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: , serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">吳留手串燒居酒屋(台中崇德店)&nbsp;</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">電話：04-22411112</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">店址：台中市北屯區崇德路二段226號</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">營業時間：PM 18：00 ～ AM 1：00</span></strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">向來是吳留手Ｆａｎｓ的我，知道崇德路開了一間二店，行程中當然要收進來一併朝聖，而且它就在金福氣南洋食堂的附近，近到你根本不用坐車，用走路就可以到ＸＤ，目前台北、台中，我是已經把所有的店都全制霸了，來到這裡，推薦明太子白醬烏龍麵、鹽烤無骨牛小排、培根捲鮮干貝、明太子雞肉串、鹽烤雞肉蔥串、一夜干午仔魚、香烤中捲、培根捲鮮蝦串及日式燒麻糬，通通都是必點的好吃！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/695/31798256375_f581141671_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">芭蕾城市渡假旅店 VillaBallet</span></strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">電話：04-35067711</span></strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">地址：台中市南屯區向上路三段221號</span></strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">官網：<a href=\"http://balletmotel.com.tw/\" style=\"color: #333333; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">http://balletmotel.com.tw/</span></a></span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">芭蕾城市渡假旅店自從開幕，就立馬掀起了一股風潮，實在是它的房型每間都美得不像話，就連商務型，也很巔覆大家的傳統印像呢！房間類型選擇豐富，就算你一個月天天都來住，也都住不完，旅店就像座大型的城堡，當你彎進向上路，馬上就會被它那霸氣十足的外型給吸引。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482389940643_355\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/528/31425866330_eed7f2c589_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482389934311_354\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/347/30957536784_c3c055a543_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">我們當天入住的是２０５伊莉莎白，最讓我著迷的，莫過於是那被拱門式羅馬建築圓柱所圍繞的大床，戶外還有一座露天式的私人游泳池，整個造景就像讓人一秒到了巴峇島，擁有滿滿的渡假風情，特別一提，這個房型還有ＫＴＶ歡唱設備、最新ZOD影片隨選系統，不管是自己情侶、夫妻獨享甜蜜時光、亦或朋友歡聚唱歌都很合適。</span><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482389926628_367\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/433/31425865850_715ac0d574_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" />&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">住宿另有提供活力早餐，是說這也太豐盛了吧！根本不用到外面覓食就能吃得很滿足。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Day2</strong></span>&nbsp;花夏入室 Fasha Room<span style=\"color: red;\">→</span>范特喜微創文化 綠光計畫<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></span></span>短腿ㄚ鹿<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></span></span>Offer Make 造堡<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></span></span>白日夢 Day Dream<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">→</span></span></span>逢甲夜市</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1476435522470_355\" src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5589/30015172800_789a089876_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-family: , serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong>花夏入室 Fasha Room&nbsp;</strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong>電話：04-23823817</strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong>店址：台中市南屯區向心路83號</strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><strong>營業時間：AM 10：00 ～ PM 18：00</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #363636; font-family: , serif; font-size: 12pt;\">在芭蕾旅店吃完早午餐，這會兒根本飽到不會想吃任何東西ＸＤ，索性把下午茶搬到中午來品嚐，而這間花夏入室，也是一開幕就立馬引起大家觀注，說它是女孩兒拍照的朝聖熱門地，可是一點也不浮誇！一進去，你會被滿滿的乾燥花給圍繞，整間店洋溢著好舒服的花香味，只要你看得到的滿天星捧花、花圈頭飾，通通都可以拿來當拍照道具呦！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1476435747200_358\" src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5441/30276892806_cbd2b29476_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" />&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1476435507078_357\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8630/30015167710_2f27e155de_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" />&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">不讓飲料專美於前，它們家的甜點也長得好可愛，價格不貴，味道也相當棒，所以會爆紅，不是沒有原因的：）</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482393788979_351\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/703/30989562203_f44db4d8a8_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a; font-size: 12pt;\">范特喜微創文化 綠光計畫</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a; font-size: 12pt;\">地址：台中市中興街一巷</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a; font-size: 12pt;\">官網：<a href=\"http://www.fantasystory.com.tw/\" style=\"color: #333333; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">http://www.fantasystory.com.tw/</span></a></span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2014年，在台中中興街一巷，有一隅文青風滿溢的文創世界正悄悄萌芽，<span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">由12間老舊員工宿舍改建而成，裡面進駐各式富含特色的小店，姿意綻放著專屬自我精采，不管是空間的設計亦或綠意花草點綴，都為這寧靜恬適的小角落，揮灑出老屋新造的創意色彩，<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">由紅磚瓦砌造而成的復古老宅，身上還攀爬著青綠藤蔓，雖然前面停放著新時代的機車產物，但仍舊遮掩不住，它那濃厚的懷舊氣味。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482394104834_365\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/482/31682750901_006957f393_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">如果認真要逛，我想一個下午的時間搞不好還不夠用呢！這個延續老宅生命力的文創世界，真的很值得走一趟細心咀嚼，雖然我不是文青，但我也愛上這兒特有的藝術氛圍。<br /><br /><ins id=\"aswift_7_expand\" style=\"border: none; display: inline-table; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 300px;\"><ins id=\"aswift_7_anchor\" style=\"border: none; display: block; height: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 300px;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"250\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_7\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_7\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"height: 250px; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 300px;\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"300\"></iframe></ins></ins>&nbsp;<ins id=\"aswift_8_expand\" style=\"border: none; display: inline-table; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 300px;\"><ins id=\"aswift_8_anchor\" style=\"border: none; display: block; height: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 300px;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"250\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"height: 250px; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 300px;\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"300\"></iframe></ins></ins></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1471829819104_361\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/9/8466/28835712180_8d1c0e7ea8_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">短腿ㄚ鹿</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">電話：04-24731978&nbsp;</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">店址：台中市南屯區大墩路311號</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">營業時間：AM 10：00 ～ PM 21：00(周日公休)</span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">這家號稱宛如香港小熊餅乾一樣好吃的「短腿ㄚ鹿」，可是現在台中相當熱門的伴手禮！剛好都在南屯區，距離范特喜也很近，建議大家可以順路過來，自己吃是享受、拿來送禮也很合適！還記得我第一口吃到時，立馬被它的濃郁奶香、鬆綿酥脆的口感給吸引，還真的很好吃耶！重點是它也好涮嘴，目前店面有開放自己手作ｄｉｙ的課程，有興趣的朋友也可以玩玩看，唯一要注意的是，它的公休日是星期天，要買的朋友可可要特別留意囉！</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482395134634_351\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/618/31760042536_3bea165e23_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #85542a; font-size: 12pt;\">Offer Make 造堡 |&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/offermakeburger\" style=\"color: #333333; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">FB</span></a></span></strong><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">電話：04-24522215</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">店址：台中市西屯區文華路150巷26號</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">營業時間：AM 11：30 ～ PM 14：30、PM 17：30 ～ PM 21：30</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">在逢甲附近，有間擁有客製化服務的美式漢堡店「Offer Make 造堡」，其實我覺得它不光是擁有好味道，在組合過程也是件新鮮又有趣的事情，Menu上所有食材，都能依自己的喜好做搭配，對向來是起司控的我，當然首選就是以起司片為主，哈哈！</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<br /></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482395903419_351\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/750/31649895772_5fe77dcb81_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">單看漢堡本人也許不明顯，沒關係，我有愛鳳當比例尺，疊起來的高度可比它還要高耶！像這樣可以豪邁吃、大口咬，就是吃漢堡最爽快的事情啦！</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">滿滿像瀑布般的澄黃顏色，光看就好滿足阿！而另一款我們則配了一個海鮮口味，大尾鮮蝦堆上去，說多霸氣就有多<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">霸氣</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>！</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482396087056_351\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/611/31649899482_aa724fb350_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">裡面的環境有著美式餐廳般的活潑風格，牆上五顏六色，感覺起來就流露著滿滿熱情氣息。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482396162339_352\" src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5597/31649899322_1664ef3bab_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">不限時、提供WIFI，只要是營業時間內，都可以很盡情地啃你的漢堡：）</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">我自己非常喜歡這區露天座椅，天氣好的時候還可以做做日光浴！</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1482396315872_351\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/287/31649896382_0d85f04651_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">不光光只有漢堡出色，其實我覺得它的水牛城雞翅也很好吃，口感鹹香入味，不用沾醬也好優秀。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">還有，汽水也是無限暢飲的呦！</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1481605424704_371\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/292/31463913272_5dcb94a46f_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">白日夢 Day Dream</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">電話：04-24521976</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">店址：台中市西屯區文華路160號</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #85542a;\">營業時間：PM 13：00 ～ PM 21：00(周二公休)</span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">白</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #85542a;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">日夢也是最近好紅的一間手搖飲料店，有著夢幻到不行的粉嫩果汁，而且整間店營造出來的氛圍也相當少女，開幕不到一個月，就變成ＩＧ上非常火紅的打卡熱點，是說逢甲這一帶，還真的藏了不少好店耶！</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" id=\"yui_3_11_0_3_1481605367757_369\" src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/710/30800838843_32165cb194_b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #1d1d1d; font-family: arial, verdana, Tahoma; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #363636; font-size: 12pt;\">熱門９４狂！當然我也要跟潮流，點個店家最夯的玫瑰樂園喝喝！事實上先不要管滋味，光是那粉粉柔柔的嬌嫩色澤，完全就是一整個療癒，呈色實在是好美好美，甜甜的莓果香還蘊含著玫瑰花氣味，喝來不甜膩、滋味還挺不錯的。<br /><br />來到這區，晚上就直接到逢甲夜市逛街覓食兼採買，說到台中有名的夜市，逢甲應該是最被人熟悉的，不少新興的小吃都從這裡發跡，不管是要買衣服、吃美食、買小雜貨，這裡通通都能滿足你的期待呦！</span></span></div>\r\n', 3, '2017-12-15', '台中3');
INSERT INTO `blog` (`Id`, `Title`, `Content`, `Member_id`, `Date`, `Pic`) VALUES
(4, '高雄這樣最好玩：旅遊路線規劃，港都吃喝玩樂', '<br />\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/f43e38af5e9f2c3b990f0a41dddbd619.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"\" width=\"640\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span><span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">美麗島捷運站</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">最近高雄捷運很精采，剛好遇到捷運動漫祭，紅線橘線都有限定的動漫列車，看是喜歡甜美可愛的高捷少女，還是熱血沸騰的草帽海賊團，想搭多久都可以啦~而且聞名國際的美麗島捷運站「光之穹頂」當然不能錯過，太漂亮了。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.07em;\">高雄西子灣捷運站挺重要，出來就是打狗鐵道故事館和駁二藝術特區，而且走路到旗津渡輪站約10分鐘，旁邊還有接駁公車可以前往打狗英國領事館唷~</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"214\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/5e2b63e14d8679c3f9ff7dfdc29297cf.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"高雄好玩卡-9.jpg\" border=\"0\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/7a55c20ea903c16fb048528279a9b92c.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"高雄好玩卡-9.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span><span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">打狗鐵道故事館</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">大片的草地很舒服，幾部已經功成身退的老火車頭停放在這裡，成了小男生最愛的遊樂場，靠近駁二倉庫的方向還放著許多大型裝置藝術，是遊客們取景拍照的好地方。如果傍晚時分靠近這裡，還會有很多爸比媽咪帶著小傢伙來這裡玩，天空會飄著很多風箏唷</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"高雄好玩卡-7.jpg\" border=\"0\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/b59f05db5af077e3793fade1802a4cfd.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"高雄好玩卡-7.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span><span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">駁二藝術特區</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">高雄駁二原本是塵封許久的老倉庫群，如今凝聚了藝術的力量重生，園區不定會期舉辦的各種展覽，繽紛又充滿創意的各種裝置藝術也會輪流在此呈現，就連五月天演唱會中的大黃蜂也在這裡，是現在來高雄必逛的景點了，逛展、拍照、看書、喝咖啡，或許找一天在這裡晃上一整天也是挺棒的玩法吧。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"高雄好玩卡-15.jpg\" border=\"0\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/b85ca79dee49daa4d4d06e40b6215834.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"高雄好玩卡-15.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span><span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">打狗英國領事館</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">雖然在古蹟喝咖啡對住台南的mimi來說沒啥吸引力，但是這裡的景色實在是太棒了，紅磚色的領事官邸，散發出濃厚的異國氣息，大高雄繁忙商港的畫面，在此可以一覽無遺，不妨點杯飲料坐下來吧!!</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"高雄好玩卡-17.jpg\" border=\"0\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/24142bcfa2b6a3c01ab3cf51431463cf.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"高雄好玩卡-17.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span><span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">旗津</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">以前都是直接開車經過港隧道前往旗津，帶著小傢伙搭渡輪還是第一次，選擇的【玩味港都逍遙遊】好玩卡，就有包含搭船的來回票，海攤、燈塔、老街、騎單車、找美食…其實旗津完全可以玩半天以上的時間唷~</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"高雄好玩卡-23.jpg\" border=\"0\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/6f5e5202a98e919989aa424308c51734.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"高雄好玩卡-23.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span><span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">搭太陽能愛之船遊愛河</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">高雄愛河兩側都有乘船的地點，分別是二二八公園和國賓大飯店旁邊，都是採用無污染零噪音的太陽能船，不會搖晃很安全，高雄的璀璨燈光一覽無遺，而且船上還會有精彩的導覽，大概25分鐘的船程，很舒服呢！比起白天，mimi感覺晚上來搭船挺不錯，不會太熱，然後燈光也更漂亮很多。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"高雄好玩卡-25.jpg\" border=\"0\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/2c3fc61d5727762240bd377461b591dd.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"高雄好玩卡-25.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span><span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">高雄市立圖書館總館</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">她是最近網友票選最新最亮眼的高雄景點了，怎麼能不來走走呢!?</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">館內藏書數量非常豐富而且多元，空間感更是明亮寬敞，在南臺灣艷陽高照的夏天，這裡無疑是個適合享受閱讀時光+吹冷氣的好地方，而且實在太漂亮了。整座建築包辦了六項國內外的NO.1，真心感覺高雄市民超幸福，讓人好羨慕呀!!</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"高雄好玩卡-44.jpg\" border=\"0\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/0e74fc1e8428668f8249b91db95fd671.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"高雄好玩卡-44.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span><span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">老江紅茶牛奶 /&nbsp;高雄市新興區南台路51號 /&nbsp;07-2877317</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">這天在離開喜八之後，還跑到附近嚐嚐六合夜市有名的老江紅茶牛奶，其實原本前一天晚上就要來逛逛六合夜市的，結果小傢伙喊腳痛，只好作罷。雖然一杯40元有點貴鬆鬆，但是看店員倒了整瓶牛奶進去，而且喝起來香濃可口，是真的挺不錯喝的好味道，生意灰熊好呢～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"高雄好玩卡-38.jpg\" border=\"0\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/7e1efd7acc10c1b3e5f6198fcdca1bae.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"高雄好玩卡-38.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span><span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">蓮池潭</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">離開橋糖，繼續搭捷運來到左營站，這裡可以轉紅51接駁公車前往蓮池潭，和印象中的景象似乎不太一樣，應該是有好好整理過了，感覺龍虎兩塔變得很漂亮，雖然現在不是蓮花季節，但池邊蓮葉很讓人期待著花朵的盛開，湖畔景點很多，除了龍虎塔之外，左營舊城、五里亭、春秋閣、啟明堂、孔廟都很近。西岸也是左營的舊市街，也是聚集著許多美食小吃，不用怕找不到食物唷~</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_7934.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/76d01700a0c32dd85a8a603628f561aa.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_7934.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span>【高雄景點】甜蜜蜜の旗津彩虹教堂：旗津貝殼博物館旁的婚攝基地，海天一色繽紛亮眼。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"旗后燈塔砲台19.JPG\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/0adfea15aca02357f5685c9644202052.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"旗后燈塔砲台19.JPG\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span>【高雄景點】必遊旗津！旗後燈塔、旗後砲台、星空隧道~ 看夕陽、欣賞大高雄港口美景~</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"高雄景點-田寮月世界31.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/5c845021ca1ba86cd4d1a91de8290a4e.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"高雄景點-田寮月世界31.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: black; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span>【高雄旅遊景點】田寮月世界地景公園：月世界也太漂亮，山谷出現天空步道，跟著嫦娥奔向月球吧</span></div>\r\n', 1, '2017-12-19', '高雄4');
INSERT INTO `blog` (`Id`, `Title`, `Content`, `Member_id`, `Date`, `Pic`) VALUES
(5, '北投市場周邊１０家必吃人氣Ｂ級美食', '<span style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , &quot;lucida grande&quot; , &quot;lucida sans&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.05px;\">大家一般來說如果搭捷運來玩，通常都會停留在新北投站附近的北投公園周邊景點，也直接在附近覓食，但其實只要多走幾步路，大概5~10分鐘就能來到「</span><strong style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.05px; margin: 0px auto;\">北投市場</strong><span style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , &quot;lucida grande&quot; , &quot;lucida sans&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.05px;\">」周邊，這裡就有好多B級美食可以享用，其中像是簡記排骨酥麵、湧蓮古早味蛋糕、蔡元益紅茶、高記茶莊．．．等，很多都是在地的人氣店家，就連在北投市場裡隨手買的胡椒餅都好好吃，而且趁著市場快收攤還能來撿便宜買水果。</span><br />\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6629-3.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/4c13a374f508ac78d1c336ea7c4de9d4.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6629-3.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲要前往<strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #e22da5; margin: 0px auto;\">北投市場</span></strong>，就從北投公園對面的麥當當、肯德基間的光明路直走，大約10分鐘就抵達<span style=\"color: #e22da5; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">北投市場</strong></span>，沿途還能買買湧蓮古早味蛋糕、明泉紅茶等美食，一路吃過去。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6628-2.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/e1f51d2615f8c046e1a8ac9a2ee36376.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6628-2.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">滿來溫泉拉麵</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：台北市北投區中山路1-8號</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：02 2894 9588</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">營業時間：11:30–21:00</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">這間超人氣的滿來溫泉拉麵就在北投公園對面，相當靠近捷運站，外面總是排著一大堆等候的人潮，非常好認。也是很多觀光客來北投玩的時候會想嘗鮮的台式拉麵店。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6631-5.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/d9dafa8a512142ba300d38a20445344e.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6631-5.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6630-4.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/0ae4e25a1e443837cda2643fd515af23.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6630-4.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲<strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">湧蓮古早味現烤蛋糕</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgba(0 , 0 , 0 , 0.87); font-family: &quot;roboto&quot; , &quot;arial&quot; , sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; margin: 0px auto;\">台北市北投區光明路200-2號</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：02－28973790</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">營業時間：10:00–22:00</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">蛋糕都是現烤出爐，有原味、起司、巧克力等四種口味，看排隊人潮就知道很厲害了，一大塊才賣120元，真的是相當平實的點心唷～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6634-6.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/6ebe8b8f4ffd0f97878039eeb231e547.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6634-6.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6639-8.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/81a45f708655acf280c87c89ddc9facd.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6639-8.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">明泉紅茶</span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：台北市北投區光明路129號</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：02－28918576</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">營業時間：08:00–22:00</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">紅茶還真的蠻好喝，仙草奶蜜．．．其實仙草奶茶囉！喝起來比較甜，但口感豐富清涼消暑。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6669-31.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/17f61ccb60f6a1070f63b014541d324f.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6669-31.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲喝完紅茶就到北投市場了，市場前就有停車場，還蠻方便的，不過我們來的時候已經稍微晚，部分店家陸續在收攤，早上倒是不知道好不好停車。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6641-10.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/c9fb01a990a948423dbd70a3857c4db3.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6641-10.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6643-12.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/87fe0bd0223c6aa3254520928b15e230.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6643-12.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲沿路兩旁就有不少店家，像是豪大雞排、林家滷味、另一邊有阿宗蚵仔煎、紅糟肉圓、花枝羹，像這種傳統市場周邊，只要有看到不少在地人在吃的店，就有很大機率不踩雷唷！哈哈，這是Mimi在台南小吃總結的心得，畢竟要在戰區存活一定要有兩把刷子的呀～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6664-27.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/f7a230fb785b633db8eaa098bf0ff679.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6664-27.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div id=\"sas_44269\" style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.91px; margin: 0px auto;\">\r\n<iframe src=\"about:blank\" style=\"height: 1px; left: -1000px; margin: 0px auto; position: absolute; width: 1px;\"></iframe></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6665-28.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/6c7fbebd241ca9f1c03b10360a0c8591.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6665-28.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6667-29.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/2131d62173e774a5dd65607dd3da576c.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6667-29.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲<strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">阿宗蚵仔煎＆春九份紅糟肉圓</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：台北市北投區磺港路20號</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：02－28981033</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">營業時間：11:00–23:00</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">兩家的口味都和台南小吃一樣甜甜的，非常合我們倆的味蕾，但這天點蝦仁煎只有６隻蝦子，不知道蚵仔煎會不會更豐富點，紅糟肉圓我喜歡~</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6647-15.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/2f2775ae526b91d3e32c98cec9a3c1e1.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6647-15.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6648-16.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/598fb249898ba5fd1eee83a5c302ea89.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6648-16.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲順著新市街走進來，就跟逛一般傳統市場一樣，兩邊都是各式攤販店家，吆喝聲此起彼落，雖然已經接近休息的時間，卻還是相當熱鬧。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6645-13.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/35e656809961478b69be54f72306d57a.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6645-13.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6646-14.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/2f640a3dcee475702a5f182de118b62c.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6646-14.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲<strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">簡記排骨酥麵</span></strong>｜<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/%E7%B0%A1%E8%A8%98%E6%8E%92%E9%AA%A8%E9%85%A5%E9%BA%B5/179183885459137?fref=ts\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：台北市北投區新市街47號</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：02-2896-1119</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">營業時間：07:00～19:30（週二休）</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">雖然已經過了中午用餐時間，但裡面人潮還是超級多，主打的排骨酥麵很受歡迎，只是環境有點不太好，但畢竟這裡是菜市場攤商，這樣也是挺有味道的囉～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6650-17.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/cc5877796ea6d0ded0ab73f63e1b2cd5.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6650-17.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6657-23.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/ed42fff9cfe8447566160a6d1a7bd35c.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6657-23.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲<strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">蔡元益紅茶</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：台北市北投區新市街15號（北投市場）</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：02－28910602</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">這家紅茶店在北投也是相當有名，而且湧蓮蛋糕、到明泉紅茶之間也有看到它的分店，這天點了杯微糖古早味紅茶還滿好喝，香氣淡雅，不過好像也差不多就是那樣^^”</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><br /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6651-18.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/57e25081c804ea07405990cd517946da.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6651-18.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6653-20.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/d73c7646827822f93bca5886f11f0843.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6653-20.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6654-21.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/49338866a61d18eaf21f993a5cac0f5c.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6654-21.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲<strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">林記胡椒餅</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">我沒有特別記住位置，大約就是在簡記排骨酥麵附近，一個推著攤車的阿伯在賣，順手買了一個來試試，可以說是很驚喜阿！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">餅皮是脆中帶嫩，口感很好，而且餡料多汁美味，咬下去時湯汁會噴出來，鹹度也調整的剛剛好，我覺得比台南的胡椒餅好吃不少，可是不知道為啥生意沒很好就是了ＸＤ</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6662-25.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/6882c5b6de2e962dc4dec4c18255336d.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6662-25.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><br /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span><br />\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6661-24.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/b6313a0cc650899eac6693c2c986ad3b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6661-24.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></span></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">\r\n</span>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲<strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">無名紅豆餅</span></strong>，紅豆奶油蘿蔔絲口味通通10元</span></span></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：台北市北投區新市街22號（鞋全家福門口）</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">賣的就是傳統的車輪餅，但一個只要10元在台北也算是相當便宜，裏頭餡料放得很紮實有誠意，還不錯吃。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"IMG_6648-16.jpg\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/598fb249898ba5fd1eee83a5c302ea89.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_6648-16.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">北投市場還有２層樓高的攤販空間，裡面除了賣生鮮肉品之外，也有好幾家北投在地美食，像是<strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">矮仔財滷肉飯、鼎邊銼雞捲、高記茶莊、阿婆麵</span></strong>都很受歡迎。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">不過我們這天來的時間稍微晚，都收得差不多了，可能要等下次再來攻略了。下次來到北投泡溫泉時，可別局限於捷運站附近找吃的，多走幾步路來試試北投市場周邊的B級美食，也是很棒的唷～</span></div>\r\n</span></div>\r\n', 2, '2017-12-17', '北投5');
INSERT INTO `blog` (`Id`, `Title`, `Content`, `Member_id`, `Date`, `Pic`) VALUES
(6, '【墾丁旅遊三天兩夜】推薦墾丁景點、必吃美食', '春天和秋天，Mimi覺得是很適合來墾丁旅遊的季節，這時南台灣天氣還不太熱，也沒有東北季風，墾丁的各景點都很舒服。所以每年春假前後，姊總會安排來趟墾丁三日遊、或是墾丁二日遊的國內旅行，但來墾丁旅遊兩三天要做啥呢？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h2 style=\"background-color: #f1f1f1; border-left: 5px solid rgb(85, 85, 85); clear: both; color: #555555; font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 23px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.91px; line-height: 1.7em; margin: 0px auto; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-left: 10px; padding-top: 2px;\">\r\n<img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/2b00520481946bbe07d9ae027caddaf8.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"\" width=\"20\" />&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\">墾丁景點</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<img alt=\"1402218545-3210774568.jpg\" height=\"563\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/6e02f84f86cd347acab33c1aa03e94a4.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1402218545-3210774568.jpg\" width=\"845\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<img alt=\"1402218547-1521485549.jpg\" height=\"564\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/6dc2d6e6ad5806aa012b9238fc1eea3f.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1402218547-1521485549.jpg\" width=\"846\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\">▲屏東海生館</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">不管是搭高鐵轉車或是自己開車，基本上來<strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">墾丁旅遊</strong>遇到第一個景點一定是「屏東海生館」，裡頭有很多豐富可愛的海洋生物，像是小白鯨、企鵝都很受歡迎，入口處還有歡樂無比的戲水場地，無論是大人還是小孩都能在這裡找到樂趣，如果時間許可的話，也可以安排「夜宿海生館體驗」，晚上帶著小朋友一起住在巨大的水槽旁邊，一大堆魚兒陪妳睡覺，肯定是很難忘的回憶。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣車城鄉後灣村後灣路2號</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：08-8825678</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<img alt=\"DSC00928-18.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/e043af105f52e86d96617ce93bbd7f56.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"DSC00928-18.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\">▲鹿境梅花鹿生態園區</span></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: 文鼎W明體M; font-size: 16px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; line-height: 27px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">這座「鹿境梅花鹿生態園區」是恆春墾丁新景點，前陣子就一直被朋友的ＦＢ燒到，誰讓梅花鹿這摸可愛啦！</span></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: 文鼎W明體M; font-size: 16px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; line-height: 27px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Mimi趁著來墾丁親子旅遊的機會，帶兄妹倆一起來玩，現在不用跑奈良，在台灣墾丁的鹿境就能感受被小鹿斑比包圍的樂趣，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">而且台灣的小鹿比較溫馴，不像奈良的鹿超兇猛，又是撞人、又是吃搶鈔票吃ＸＤ</span></span></div>\r\n<div class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: 文鼎W明體M; font-size: 16px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; line-height: 27px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮南灣路728號</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">電話：08-888-1940</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">營業時間：09:00~17:00</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">票價：全票$200；優待票$50；５歲以下免費（全票可以換三選一優惠，見文內）</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<ins id=\"aswift_4_expand\" style=\"background-color: transparent; border: none; display: inline-table; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 336px;\"><ins id=\"aswift_4_anchor\" style=\"background-color: transparent; border: none; display: block; height: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 336px;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"280\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_4\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_4\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"height: 280px; left: 0px; margin: 0px auto; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 336px;\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"336\"></iframe></ins></ins></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"1440950255-2759821707.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/8060b3247f3051e18f22c709149b658e.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1440950255-2759821707.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"1440950244-3406898113.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/11471ecc9f690bfbfc6103102d39e578.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1440950244-3406898113.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\">▲阿信巧克力農場</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">這座《阿信巧克力農場》位置就在悠活度假村對面，裏頭有許多挺有意思的活動，像是香草精油DIY、巧克力生態DIY，都讓我們都留下開心的回憶，門票也是全額抵消費，是挺適合順遊的親子景點。</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">而且建議可以安排直接入住悠活渡假村（<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/partners/partnersearch.aspx?cid=1640859&amp;pcs=1&amp;hid=60400\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #e22da5; margin: 0px auto;\">查房價</span></a>），飯店有兒童旅館的房型，大小泳池、鄰近海灘等設施，不用出門就能玩得很盡興～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮萬里路27-9號</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：08-8869696</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\">夏季(5-10月) 週一到週日 09:00至19:00</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\">冬季(11-4月) 週一到週日 09:00至18:00</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<img alt=\"DSC00766-1.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/621b5238721d63aad1aa8a2d8f5adab3.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"DSC00766-1.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\">▲關山日落</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">南臺灣墾丁的關山日落，被美國CNN評選為「全球12最美夕陽之一」，在台灣就能看到國際級的美景，怎麼能錯過呢？</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">也提醒大家，現在關山觀景台要收門票（60元／人），建議大家可以斟酌當天的天空，感覺有夕陽再去就好，不然會有浪費錢的感覺。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣恒春鎮（GPS定位：關山日落景觀台）</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\">開放時間：9月～3月 09:00~18:30；4月～8月 09:00~19:00</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"1446199707-1141859929.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/a435d51da76d38c67fd42f18620a6334.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1446199707-1141859929.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"1446199708-1931583254.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/1422845c99a90bd8b2f5e282fcf7607e.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1446199708-1931583254.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲白沙灣海灘</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">自從李安導演的少年Pi 電影之後，墾丁的白沙灣就成了更多人會喜歡來的地方，這裡比起南灣、船帆石等海灘，這裡的遊客較少，而且外面就是露營區，喜歡露營的朋友可以安排在這裡紮營。而如果想要找民宿，那附近的－海灣森林精品民宿非常值得推薦，裏頭空間使用大量原木家具，光聞檜木香就是種享受，而且更棒的是房間就有無敵海景，幾乎住過都說棒~</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"1386683387-2877580905.jpg\" height=\"564\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/c25b6b8f74dd3736cebd4950c7a4fd30.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1386683387-2877580905.jpg\" width=\"846\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲龍磐公園</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">這趟來到龍磐草原，剛好迎著太平洋強勁的東北季風，讓人連站穩腳步都不容易，但是這裡居高臨下的遼闊視野，依然讓人沉醉在這樣海天一色的畫面之中。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"1470837658-2342934794.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/d5dce350fe8adefa8c1edb20bbea30b9.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1470837658-2342934794.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\">▲勁風甩尾場</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">墾丁的『勁風甩尾場』位於恆春的恆公路上，就是通過恆春市區外圍的這條。對面是雲起會館，大大的看板稍微注意一下應該不會找不到。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">雖說附近其實賽車場還不少，但是勁風的卡丁車是裡面最有特色的，甩尾超有感，是比較刺激的墾丁旅遊玩法，大人小孩幾乎玩過都說讚唷～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮恆公路123號</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：0937 – 796479</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">營業時間：&nbsp;8:30 ~ 20:30</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<img alt=\"DSC00999-5.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/f8d1ba502f7919695114f4ae80634034.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"DSC00999-5.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲恆春3000啤酒博物館</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">這座「恆春3000啤酒博物館」是去年才開幕的新墾丁景點，裏頭並不大，最有特色的是那幅用酒標拼成的蒙娜麗莎，還有那片用一大堆酒杯組成的牆，都成了時下IG打卡的熱門景點。二樓展示著許多與啤酒、釀酒相關的歷史文物與資訊，參觀門票可以抵用消費。午後天氣太熱的話，可以來這裡走走，點杯啤酒、可樂幫自己消暑一下。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮草埔路29-1號</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：08-8881002</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\">門票：印象中是100元，只有18歲以上才需要門票，可抵用飲料消費。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<img alt=\"IMG_26051.JPG\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/5ff36851ed1ff7d1a66f8f9a0d321334.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"IMG_26051.JPG\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲阿嘉の家</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電影海角七號當時真的是成功帶動了墾丁的觀光旅遊，而「海角七號」主角阿嘉的家就在恆春老街，門口擺著紀念品與明信片，進入參觀要消費50元，小小的景點，旅人卻還是不少，而對面的老屋，也就是最近很有名的迷路餐桌計畫－波波廚房，兩個地方都很值得一逛一吃唷～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮光明路90號</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：08－8892585</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"1399982537-4121341470.jpg\" height=\"567\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/e91814e2111adc815db8d390ec786b06.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1399982537-4121341470.jpg\" width=\"851\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲南灣海灘、船帆石海灘</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">墾丁的海灘有好幾個，像南灣、船帆石的沙灘都是很熱門的地方，也有像砂島那樣的珊瑚礁岸，在海邊除了熱情的陽光，更棒的是可以欣賞墾丁的無敵海景。不過因為附近實在沒看到救生員，建議如果是小朋友的話還是在岸邊玩沙就好，簡單買組玩沙工具、水槍就玩翻天了，不然也別真的離岸太遠唷！</span></div>\r\n<h2 style=\"background-color: #f1f1f1; border-left: 5px solid rgb(85, 85, 85); clear: both; color: #555555; font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 23px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.91px; line-height: 1.7em; margin: 0px auto; padding-bottom: 2px; padding-left: 10px; padding-top: 2px;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: red; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/3be83147c14d3593d8daa1665d46b3f8.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"\" width=\"20\" />&nbsp;墾丁美食</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"1485853782-1518993416.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/da68bce40f0a0cf59ff4d86836ab881f.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1485853782-1518993416.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲迷路餐桌計畫</strong>－<strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">波波廚房</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">最近墾丁美食界，掀起一陣迷路系列旋風，其中恆春鎮阿嘉的家旁邊的「波波廚房」就是非常熱門的迷路系列餐廳。姊趁著來墾丁的機會，當然要給它收藏起來，外觀是漂亮的巴洛克式老建築，裏頭一樓結合了窯烤麵包、冰淇淋、咖啡店、老書店的複合式空間，二樓則是提供異國料理的「波波廚房」，老屋改造的的空間相當具有質感，雖然餐點價格稍高，但從環境、餐點到氣氛，都讓人會愛上她呢～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮光明路88號 （阿嘉的家旁)</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">電話：(08)889-6575</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<img alt=\"1447760883-1237105977.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/9f6905c8ba05133b81374f02fc1d18e9.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1447760883-1237105977.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲</strong></span></span><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">白羊道柴燒麻糬</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">這間麻糬姊竟然跑了三次才吃到，感覺自己在台南找美食都沒那麼積極，第一次沒搞清楚營業時間太早來，第二次人太多等不下去，再接再厲的第三趟終於達成任務。很喜歡這裡四顆不同顏色的麻糬，搭配一罐玻璃瓶裝的冷泡花茶，盤飾還真的挺漂亮，看起來心情就很好，麻糬口感軟綿綿，卻又帶著適當的嚼勁，越咬越香，還蠻好吃ㄟ。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮中山路188號</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：08-8899992、0960-100260</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">營業時間：13：30～賣完為止（大約6-7點）</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">週二、週三、週四公休</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<ins id=\"aswift_9_expand\" style=\"background-color: transparent; border: none; display: inline-table; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 336px;\"><ins id=\"aswift_9_anchor\" style=\"background-color: transparent; border: none; display: block; height: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 336px;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"280\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_9\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_9\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"height: 280px; left: 0px; margin: 0px auto; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 336px;\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"336\"></iframe></ins></ins></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"DSC08312-1.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/3fab26599ce781b71e61cf067e6d349e.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"DSC08312-1.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"DSC08367-27.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/496a8a558cc81a20b67acc899410cb15.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"DSC08367-27.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲迷路小章魚</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">最近的墾丁美食掀起一股迷路餐桌風，而其中『迷路小章魚&nbsp;Piccolo Polpo Bistro』和位於恆春的『波波廚房（點我看文）』被很多網友說是來墾丁必吃的迷路系列餐酒館，當然也得來朝聖看看才行，而這家「迷路小章魚」隔一條馬路對面就是南灣海灘，沙灘、陽光、大陸客（比基尼最近都看不到惹）都盡收眼底，店裡充滿地中海氣息的陳設，還有細選食材，新鮮現做的各種料理菜色，除了貴了點之外，真的是挺棒的選擇，覓食去吧～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮南灣里南灣路68號</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">電話：08-8882822</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">營業時間：12:00~15:00；17:30~21:00（週三休）</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<img alt=\"DSC00888-3.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/eeb1d02d9de6621da6fabb1906486f3c.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"DSC00888-3.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲阿利海產</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">這家阿利海產在墾丁後壁湖，是當地很有名氣的美食餐廳，外面有很大的停車場，裡面的料理都是現點現做，海鮮非常新鮮。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">而且座位非常多，很適合人多的時候來，不過我們今天兩大兩小也是吃得很開心啦～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮砂尾路20之1號</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：08－8866479</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">營業時間：11:00～15:00；17:00～21:00</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<ins id=\"aswift_10_expand\" style=\"background-color: transparent; border: none; display: inline-table; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 336px;\"><ins id=\"aswift_10_anchor\" style=\"background-color: transparent; border: none; display: block; height: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 336px;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"280\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_10\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_10\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"height: 280px; left: 0px; margin: 0px auto; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 336px;\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"336\"></iframe></ins></ins></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"565\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/0477d29dfe555a65c10392b67b7fa7cf.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"\" width=\"848\" />​</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲阿伯綠豆饌</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">在恆春綠豆饌似乎是蠻受歡迎的墾丁美食，在恆春老街上有好幾間都在賣，秉持著「不知道吃哪間，就找人最多的那間」為原則，遠遠就看到這間【阿伯綠豆饌】了，她店門口有長長的人潮啊，尤其是夏天很推薦要吃冰的，喝下去通體舒暢，超涼爽的。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮中山路11號</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：08-8898918</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">營業時間：10:00 ~ 19:00</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">​<img alt=\"阿伯綠豆饌16.JPG\" border=\"0\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/a58775cfff7886e75e1082bdd31f059b.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"阿伯綠豆饌16.JPG\" width=\"842\" />​</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲玉珍香手工蛋捲</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">玉珍香從1919年創立，到現在可是一間已經有百年歷史的老字號了，店裡頭主要賣的就是手工蛋捲，看工作人員很多，就知道生意一定相當好，可惜店內不准拍攝，只能自己想像囉！一打開夾鏈袋，裡頭蛋捲加上洋蔥的濃郁香氣就散發出來，吃起來口感很酥鬆，層次感也很棒，是很好吃的蛋捲無誤。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮中山路80號</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：08-8892272 (本店)</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">營業時間：08:00 ~ 21:00</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<img alt=\"1485853778-1572940285.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/06f17998ca9d360da6b39dbcdf6c7250.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1485853778-1572940285.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲沃土Gelato義式冰淇淋</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">這間冰淇淋和波波廚房在同一個老屋中，口味都是以當季季節水果為主，輕甜不膩口，正適合四季如夏的墾丁天氣，來到墾丁，不妨來份沃土Gelato的義式冰淇淋吧！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮光明路88號 （阿嘉的家旁)</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">電話：(08)889-6575</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<img alt=\"DSC01018-6.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/449f4c0e0c029acb4502c6cbbac36a29.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"DSC01018-6.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\">▲東港餃子館</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">雖然招牌掉了，但還是非常有人氣的墾丁在地美食唷！其實就有點像是傳統麵館，但店家自己包的水餃又大又好吃，一個才賣６塊錢，大魚大肉吃多了，換個口味也挺好。但我是覺得除了水餃之外其他都還好，像是酸辣麵沒啥酸辣味，而滷菜也是相當清淡的口感，不過畢竟口味見仁見智很主觀，也是可以品嘗看看唷～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span class=\"auto_font_family_setting\" style=\"font-family: 文鼎w明體m; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣恆春鎮恆公路688號</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：08 889 9575</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"1471242834-1740921476.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/e11be1d31c953d7073dd8def247d5af8.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"1471242834-1740921476.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: blue; margin: 0px auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px auto;\">▲好樂冰杯</strong></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">彷彿只要有朋友要去墾丁玩耍，這間『好樂冰杯』就必定會出現她的ＦＢ打卡動態上，熱門的程度實在驚人，好樂冰杯就開在屏鵝公路的屏東枋山路段，大概就在枋山休息站附近，是大家要去墾丁必定會經過的地方，很適合當成旅行中休息站。走進店門的瞬間，這座好像隨意拼湊的木造平房，會讓人真的有一種瞬間飛到南洋海島的錯覺。坐下來點杯冰沙，放空凝視著台灣海峽，聽著海浪規律的聲音，舒服極了呢～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地址：屏東縣枋山鄉枋山村中山路三段29號</span></span><span style=\"color: #b41a0f; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">電話：08 – 8761082</span></span></div>\r\n', 2, '2017-12-23', '墾丁6');
INSERT INTO `blog` (`Id`, `Title`, `Content`, `Member_id`, `Date`, `Pic`) VALUES
(7, '【墾丁住宿推薦】擁抱無敵海景！必住10間墾丁海景民宿', '<span style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.05px;\">每年春天和秋天，Mimi就會想來墾丁享受屬於我們國境之南的大海，這時候只要挑幾間有絕美海景的墾丁民宿或墾丁住宿，再安排像浮潛、踏浪等水上活動，就是一個很美很棒的墾丁假期。這篇「墾丁海景民宿筆記」推薦的10間墾丁民宿，都是Mimi曾經住過或目前關注的口袋名單，像是白沙灣的海灣森林，後壁湖的聽靜海、墾丁大街的冒煙的喬、船帆石的白水木、姊妹沙灘別墅．．．幾乎每間都有超美的房型、無敵的海景，卻只要相對飯店更平實的房價，CP值真的很高，如果不想住大型飯店的話，這10間墾丁民宿絕對是很棒的住宿選擇。ＧＯＧＯＯＧＯ～來去墾丁享受碧海藍天吧～</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.05px;\"><br /></span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.05px;\">這篇１０間墾丁民宿，主要坐落在白沙灣、後壁湖、墾丁大街、船帆石和鵝鑾鼻等大家常去的地點，民宿雖然沒辦法提供像飯店一樣休憩設施，但因為附近都有沙灘可以玩水，一樣很棒。簡單標示地圖，在安排旅行時，大家可以自己對照一下差不多的位置唷！來點點名吧~</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.05px;\"><br /></span>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">1.海灣森林精品民宿 (Bay Forest Boutique Guesthouse)→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/bay-forest-boutique-guesthouse/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/bay-forest-boutique-hotel.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"11.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/e8100b2bf4f47cdd10bd2d5548ee42c4.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"11.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲海灣森林精品民宿→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/bay-forest-boutique-guesthouse/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/bay-forest-boutique-hotel.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">Agoda評價8.8分；Booking.com評價9.1分</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">海灣森林精品民宿在白沙灣海灘附近，開車大概３分鐘就到了，整個民宿綠地很多，空間使用大量原木家具，光聞檜木香就是種享受，更棒的是房間就有無敵海景。雖然說是民宿，但它的質感絕對比得上會館的等級。或者說是好野人的私人招待所，大概也差不多就這樣了吧！晚餐可以選擇前往墾丁大街或是恆春市區覓食，也能直接在民宿裡的森食堂餐廳用餐，詳細菜單請參考→【<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://issuu.com/bayforest5/docs/_______4694616e1b037a\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">電子菜單</a>】</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">參考價位：2763元</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地理位置：位於墾丁很熱門的白沙灣海灘不遠處，有免費自行車租借服務</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">圖文：<a data-wpel-link=\"internal\" href=\"https://mimihan.tw/2015-11-01-868/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">【墾丁民宿】海灣森林精品民宿：白沙灣旁海景無敵，原木風格溫暖簡約。</a></span></div>\r\n<hr style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.91px; margin: 0px auto;\" />\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">2.聽靜海休閒會館 (Leisure Lulu Villa)→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/leisure-lulu-villa/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/leisureluluvilla.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"12.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/167eebcffe2ac393a097492ac623411a.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"12.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲聽靜海休閒會館→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/leisure-lulu-villa/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/leisureluluvilla.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">Agoda評價8.1分；Booking.com評價8.5分</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">LuLu聽靜海休閒會館在後壁湖附近，可以去漁港美食街覓食，房型分Villa四人房和海景雙人房，充滿南國風格，還有游泳池唷！椰子樹、茅草屋、木雕裝飾，不用出國就能享受那種慵懶的南洋度假氣息。懶得跑恆春或大街覓食的話，這裡有供應餐點，以套餐的方式出餐，主廚會隨著季節改變菜色，訂房時最好一起預定。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">參考價位：2013元</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地理位置：位於墾丁後壁湖這裡，地勢較高，在會館廣場，可以很輕鬆的眺望湛藍海洋，美翻了!</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">圖文：<a data-wpel-link=\"internal\" href=\"https://mimihan.tw/2015-11-09-874/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">【墾丁住宿推薦】LuLu Villa 聽靜海休閒會館：後壁湖旁，滿滿南洋島國氣息</a></span></div>\r\n<hr style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.91px; margin: 0px auto;\" />\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">3.快樂小鎮休閒度假民宿 (Happy Town Resort)→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/happy-town-resort/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/kuai-le-xiao-zhen.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"13.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/3d8cb0c45c6f51c043ac89b7bc05b39e.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"13.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲快樂小鎮休閒度假民宿→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/happy-town-resort/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/kuai-le-xiao-zhen.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">Agoda評價8.1分；Booking.com評價8.5分</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">快樂小鎮走的就是濃濃的藍白色地中海希臘風格，如果你很喜歡藍白色地中海希臘風，那麼一定要來住住啦！就位在後壁湖漁港附近，除了有好吃的海鮮，從這裡也可以搭船去綠島，無敵海景很美，腹地很大，民宿最近加建了婚禮建設和白色風車，感覺更美更夢幻，可作結婚場地。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">參考價位：2208元</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地理位置：位於大光，後壁湖漁港附近山坡上，視野很棒。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">4.墾丁南灣Just Hi海景民宿 (Just Hi Seaview B&amp;B)→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/just-hi-seaview-b-b/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"14.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/753b32cbcff172f660b147000b35d301.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"14.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲墾丁南灣Just Hi海景民宿→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/just-hi-seaview-b-b/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">Agoda評價8.9分</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">墾丁南灣沙灘的美景就在眼前，房間和環境給人舒服自在的氛圍，無論在房間或樓下餐廳吃早餐的位置都看的到海景。共有11間房間，除了後方的小屋四人房之外，其它每個房間都是海景房，走路5分鐘左右就可到南灣玩沙，距離墾丁大街約５分鐘車程。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">參考價位：2771元</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地理位置：鄰近南灣沙灘，租車或是機場接送也能提供協助</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">圖文：<a data-wpel-link=\"internal\" href=\"https://mimihan.tw/2017-04-02-1499/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"墾丁住宿》南灣Just Hi就是海民宿，擁抱墾丁無敵海景，南灣海灘走路５分鐘～\">墾丁住宿》南灣Just Hi就是海民宿，擁抱墾丁無敵海景，南灣海灘走路５分鐘～</a></span></div>\r\n<hr style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.91px; margin: 0px auto;\" />\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">5.冒煙的喬 雅客旅店 (Smokey Joe’s Hotel)→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/smokey-joe-s-hotel/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/smokey-joes.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"15.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/01cb2fe97fbd142557f2fa63051b4c06.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"15.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲冒煙的喬 雅客旅店→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/smokey-joe-s-hotel/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/smokey-joes.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">Agoda評價9.0分；Booking.com評價9.1分</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">冒煙的喬雖然不是民宿，不過我覺得還是想把它收錄起來，走美式風格，高格調的年輕人旅館太美了，經常播放著怡情的音樂丶歌曲，很有渡假感覺！再加上地點很方便，外面就是超熱鬧的墾丁大街，不過飯店隔音做的挺好。另外設有游泳池，沙灘也就在附近，玩沙玩水都很方便！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">參考價位：3275元</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地理位置：位於墾丁大街，走路&nbsp;2 分鐘可抵達海灘。</span></div>\r\n<hr style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.91px; margin: 0px auto;\" />\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">6.姊妹沙灘別墅 (Four Sisters Villa)→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/four-sisters-villa/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/zi-mei-sha-tan-bie-shu.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"16.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/ec6a632fa7aa287f726aad566144712f.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"16.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲姊妹沙灘別墅→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/four-sisters-villa/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/zi-mei-sha-tan-bie-shu.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">Agoda評價9.1分；Booking.com評價9.5分</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">姊妹沙灘別墅是近期評價超高的墾丁住宿，因為房間真的美到沒朋友的程度，根本就像住在私人度假別墅般啊！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">房間處處有巧思，整體設計全都走超質感路線，每間房間擁有不同的樣貌，讓旅人們可以依照自己喜好去挑選，環境清幽，不會吵雜，外面就是船帆石海灘，而且別墅距離墾丁大街也不遠，還提供接駁車服務，大廳還有自助式下午茶讓人免費享用，讓人有旅遊的幸福感，大推薦～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">參考價位：3958元</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地理位置：位於鵝鑾鼻的船帆石沙灘對面，墾丁福華飯店旁。</span></div>\r\n<hr style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.91px; margin: 0px auto;\" />\r\n<div id=\"sas_44269\" style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.91px; margin: 0px auto;\">\r\n<span id=\"sas_advDiv_7462081\" style=\"clear: both; color: #cccccc; display: block; font-famil