e: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/bai-shui-mu-shui-yang-hui-guan-bai-shuei-mu-inn.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"17.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/54be24edae2674f234c2ea1b07254e54.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"17.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲白水木水漾會館→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/bai-shuei-mu-inn/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/bai-shui-mu-shui-yang-hui-guan-bai-shuei-mu-inn.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">Agoda評價9.1分；Booking.com評價9.1分</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">白水木水漾會館剛開的時候mimi就去住過惹，地點就在墾丁船帆石海灘對面，兩棟純白色的主建築在燈光的投射之下，散發著高貴的氣息，有著極美好的休憩環境與主人親切的待客之道，走到船帆石海灘，更有著墾丁專屬的一切天然與美麗。不用花俏、沒有繽紛，就像是天空上的白雲，那麼的舒服自然。而且使用的材料質感都很棒，讓人有種走進豪宅的感覺，房間也很美唷～</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">參考價位：3275元</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地理位置：走下斜坡，對面就是船帆石海灘</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">圖文：<a data-wpel-link=\"internal\" href=\"https://mimihan.tw/2013-12-14-348/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">【墾丁住宿推薦】白水木水漾會館，酒店般的客房、民宿般的款待，鄰船帆石海灘，天然美景自取。</a></span></div>\r\n<hr style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.91px; margin: 0px auto;\" />\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">8.靜觀行館 (Jing Guan Hotel)→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/jing-guan-hotel/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/jing-guan-xing-guan.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"18.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/f4d51a899946dd23956918419b96314c.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"18.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲靜觀行館→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/jing-guan-hotel/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/jing-guan-xing-guan.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">Agoda評價9.0分</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">行館對面就是帆船石景點，隔街就是大海，坐擁無敵海景！外觀以清水模打造，內裝走的是南洋風格,每個房間都能夠直接面海，有電梯，房間很大，環境優靜，特別是浴缸對著海，超正的！有免費洗衣服務，有專車去幾個景點和墾丁大街來回，這樣其實也省下很多。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">參考價位：2698元</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地理位置：位於墾丁的船帆石</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">9.洋老院 (West Old House)→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/west-old-house/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"19.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/b7f483fe8738a3698716010388a79501.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"19.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲洋老院→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/west-old-house/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">Agoda評價8.6分</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">洋老院位置於山坡上，開車較佳！可以直接看到海，遠方也可以看到鵝鑾鼻燈塔，相當悠哉的住宿地點，旁邊就是草原及大海，1層樓共有7個房間，空間挺寬敞，鵝黃的色調搭配著異國風格，讓人很有置身國外的渡假氛圍，晚上如果不想去外面用餐，民宿也有提供無菜單套餐，只是要記得提早預訂唷~</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">參考價位：2597元</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地理位置：位於風景優美的鵝鑾鼻地區，恆春鎮埔頂路上。</span></div>\r\n<hr style=\"color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.91px; margin: 0px auto;\" />\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">10.墾丁國境之南設計旅店 (Kenting South Border DeSign Hotel)→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/kenting-south-border-design-hotel/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/south-border-design-hotel.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><img alt=\"20.jpg\" src=\"https://img.mimihan.tw/pixnet/58c226f0a70a7b98ce9f6598a6aed935.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; height: auto; margin: 0px auto; max-width: 750px;\" title=\"20.jpg\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">▲墾丁國境之南設計旅店→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/kenting-south-border-design-hotel/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/south-border-design-hotel.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">Agoda評價8.5分；Booking.com評價8.3分</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">十分舒適的度假風格設計，夜晚頂樓的觀景台能看到無限的星海，擁有極為美好的戶外風光，與墾丁特殊的悠閒氣氛結合，絕對是很棒的度假選擇，但因為距離墾丁大街較遠，所以飲食較為不便。 房間的裝潢設計也十分地充滿度假風格，當天氣好時遠眺海洋，那絕對是種美好的享受！</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">參考價位：2116元</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">地理位置：位於風景優美的鵝鑾鼻地區，距離墾丁大街大約有15分鐘的車程，有免費接駁車服務。</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><ins id=\"aswift_8_expand\" style=\"background-color: transparent; border: none; display: inline-table; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 336px;\"><ins id=\"aswift_8_anchor\" style=\"background-color: transparent; border: none; display: block; height: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 336px;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"280\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"height: 280px; left: 0px; margin: 0px auto; position: absolute; top: 0px; width: 336px;\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"336\"></iframe></ins></ins></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">最後再把這篇墾丁住宿由西到東的地點整理一下，大家可以看喜歡的地點直接點選。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">白沙灣</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">海灣森林精品民宿 (2763元 )→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/bay-forest-boutique-guesthouse/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/bay-forest-boutique-hotel.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">後壁湖</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">聽靜海休閒會館 (2013元 )→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/leisure-lulu-villa/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/leisureluluvilla.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\">快樂小鎮休閒度假民宿 (2208元 )→&nbsp;<a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.agoda.com/zh-hk/happy-town-resort/hotel/kenting-tw.html?cid=1640859\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #0066cc; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Agoda訂房</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;、<span style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto;\"><a data-wpel-link=\"external\" href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/tw/kuai-le-xiao-zhen.zh-tw.html?aid=1287856\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow external\" style=\"color: #ff6600; margin: 0px auto; outline: none medium; text-decoration-line: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Booking.com訂房</a></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"border: 0px none; color: #555555; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-stretch: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 27px; margin: 15px auto;\">\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; margin: 0px auto;\"><span style=\"background-color: yellow; margin: 0px auto;\">